de.tuberlin.dima.bdapro.dataIntegration.weather

Class WeatherReadingParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tuberlin.dima.bdapro.dataIntegration.weather.WeatherReadingParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class WeatherReadingParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The WeatherReadingParser splits data from the weather input data from OpenWeatherMap web APIs and generates WeatherReading. It sets all valid features to their appropriate values and leaves the rest null. The logic of each field is specified in Field
